#general-page-app
  / 必要的共用組件
  = render 'share/components'

  .content
    .static-head.d-flex
      .title
        創辦歷程
      .decoration-line

    .static-body
      .row
        // 中文
        .body-description.col-md-6.col-12
          .description-title
            創辦歷程
          .description-body.mt-3
            %div
              當我們還是孩子的時候，
              每天醒來整個屋子裡總是瀰漫著咖啡的香氣，
              這是讓我們最難以忘懷的記憶。
              我們對咖啡的熱愛也是從那個時候便開始，
              那是我們日常生活的一部分。
            %br
            %div
              在歷經幾次工作搬遷後我們認識了台灣，
              我們認為台灣是一個友善、美好的地方，
              也希望我們的孩子能在這裡成長為一位善良的人。
            %br
            %div
              在這裡生活了兩年，
              發現大家對咖啡的需求普遍依賴連鎖企業，
              而我們則想起了兒時祖父沖煮咖啡的記憶。
              那麼新鮮、那麼溫暖。
            %br
            %div
              我們想讓大家知道，精品咖啡並非遙遠，
              只要你願意，我們提供你這些讓我們引以為傲得豆子，讓大家可以簡單、方便地享用。
              “You deserve a fresh, finest cup of coffee.”
            %br
            %div
              我們懷著感恩的心繼續生活在這片土地，
              並且對您保證能從家族的莊園帶來品質最好的咖啡豆，
              這是我們能為我們所愛的土地盡的一份努力。與台灣這片美好的土地交流。
        // 英文
        .body-description.col-md-6.col-12
          .description-title
            The Story Behind Our Story
          .description-body.mt-3
            %div
              Our love for coffee started when we were kids.  Growing up in Panama had printed the unforgettable memory of waking up by the smell of freshly brewed coffee by grandpa.
            %br
            %div
              After living abroad for so many years, we visited Taiwan and we fell in love with the island and its people.  — We decided to call Taiwan home and raise our two boys  in This beautiful island to learn the language and the rich culture Taiwan has to offer.
            %br
            %div
              Although been away for Panama for almost 20 years, there are some unerasable memories, and despite the huge coffee culture in Taiwan, There was one thing we couldn’t get used to —the struggle for a good cup of coffee.  The struggle to find fresh and well brewed coffee as our grandfather used to express without words was real.  Therefore we decided to bring directly from our family farm the finest and most delicious coffee we have to offer because everybody on the island deserve coffee roasted and brewed with passion.
            %br
              We are forever grateful to the place we call home and its people, and the least we can do is to share the finest coffee from our hometown.
